{{Infobox dungeon |name = Union Cave |image = [[File:Union Cave.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Union Cave. |tokens = 3,000 |location = South of Violet City and the [[Ruins of Alph]], on Route 32. }} '''Union Cave''' is a dungeon in [[Johto]]. It initially has 36 tiles arranged in an 6x6 square, including 6 chest tiles, 14 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
